  Hi! First of all - you do a great job, I love p10k.
  
  I have a question - is it possible to change prompt transience dynamically (using some keyboard shortcut)? I'm afraid it's not possible, but let me explain my reasoning.
  
  Full prompt (i.e. two liner) looks great and I would really appreciate to work with that. But, on the other hand, when copying and pasting terminal, it looks terrible, so for commands results it is better to keep it simple. So for now i can't use full prompt, but it would be awesome if I can switch view dynamically (shrink just to copy and then return to full version).
  
  Thanks in advance :)
  
