  # [We may have killed p10k, so I found the perfect replacement.](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9U8LCjuQzdc)
  
  **Visibility**: Public
  **Uploaded by**: [Dreams of Autonomy](http://www.youtube.com/@dreamsofautonomy)
